</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<p>Regions of direct illumination and shadow on the Grand Canyon</p>
</div>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 28px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Set06-DSC07722-a.jpg" class="image" title="Set06-DSC07722-a.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/15/Set06-DSC07722-a.jpg/120px-Set06-DSC07722-a.jpg" width="120" height="90" border="0" /></a></div>
